   <text>
      <body divRole="original-translation">
         <div type="original" xml:lang="nl">
            <pb xml:id="pb.orig.nl.1" f="1r" facs="#s1r" n="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.1" n="1">Woensdag</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.2" n="2">Beste Jo,</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.3" n="3">Vrijdag is de begrafenis v. <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#pers014">Blommers</rs>,<ptr type="note" target="#note.orig.nl.1"/> ik kom dan later te Amst. Ik zal je nog wel schrijven wanneer. Ofschoon ik <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#pers014">Blommers</rs> nooit zag<ptr type="note" target="#note.orig.nl.2"/> is het toch een gemis omdat ik hem zoo lang gekend heb.– Gelukkig dat ’t met <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#pers128">Vincent</rs> goed <pb f="1v" facs="#s1v" n="2"/> gaat. Zeg hem dat ik hem gauw in ieder geval kom opzoeken. Hartelijke groeten, ook aan  <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#pers078">Jos</rs>,<ptr type="note" target="#note.orig.nl.3"/> en tot spoedig!</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.4" n="4" rend="indent">Steeds,</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.5" n="5">Yours</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.6" n="6">I.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <pb xml:id="pb.orig.nl.3" f="2r" facs="#s2r" n="3"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.7" n="7">Mevrouw Cohen Gosschalk</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.8" n="8">Koninginneweg 77</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.9" n="9">Amsterdam</p>
            <pb xml:id="pb.orig.nl.4" f="2v" facs="#s2v" n="4"/>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            <pb xml:id="pb.tr.en.1"
                corresp="#pb.orig.nl.1"
                f="1r"
                facs="#s1r"
                n="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.1" corresp="#p.orig.nl.1" n="1">Wednesday</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.2" corresp="#p.orig.nl.2" n="2">Dear Jo,</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.3" corresp="#p.orig.nl.3" n="3">Friday is <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#pers014">Blommers</rs>’s funeral,<ptr type="note" target="#note.tr.en.1"/> so I’ll be later coming to Amst. I’ll write and let you know when. Although I never saw <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#pers014">Blommers</rs>,<ptr type="note" target="#note.tr.en.2"/> it’s still a loss because I knew him for so long.– It’s fortunate that <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#pers128">Vincent</rs>’s doing <pb f="1v" facs="#s1v" n="2"/> well. Tell him that I shall come and see him soon in any event. Warmest wishes, to  <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#pers078">Jos</rs> too,<ptr type="note" target="#note.tr.en.3"/> and see you soon!</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.4" corresp="#p.orig.nl.4" n="4" rend="indent">Ever,</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.5" corresp="#p.orig.nl.5" n="5">Yours</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.6" corresp="#p.orig.nl.6" n="6">I.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <pb xml:id="pb.tr.en.3"
                corresp="#pb.orig.nl.3"
                f="2r"
                facs="#s2r"
                n="3"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.7" corresp="#p.orig.nl.7" n="7">Mevrouw Cohen Gosschalk</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.8" corresp="#p.orig.nl.8" n="8">Koninginneweg 77</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.9" corresp="#p.orig.nl.9" n="9">Amsterdam</p>
            <pb xml:id="pb.tr.en.4"
                corresp="#pb.orig.nl.4"
                f="2v"
                facs="#s2v"
                n="4"/>
         </div>
